Hazel Henderson:

"Ethical Markets’ Green Transition Scoreboard has become a focal point for private retail and institutional investors to analyze the growth of green sectors and deepen their due diligence using updated asset valuation models (Updating Fossilized Asset-Allocation Classes).  It provides a guide to the winning technologies that are part of the evolutionary succession from the 300 years of fossil-fueled Industrial Age to the cleaner, greener, information-rich Solar Age.  We have recommended that pension funds and other institutional investors shift at least 10% of their portfolios away from risky hedge funds and commodity ETFs to investments in growing green companies."
(http://www.ethicalmarkets.com/2011/06/17/from-potemkin-carbon-markets-to-direct-investments-in-growing-low-carbon-economies/)

